{
  "stem": "5496.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know who they were, but all-- we heard them yelling in all kind of languages, they-- give the children to the old.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Give the children to the old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, being that we didn't have small children, we were one group.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The next thing we know, my father was gone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We never had a chance to say goodbye.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He disappeared, and the next thing we know is, we were standing in front of the infamous Dr.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Mengele, and my grandmother to the left, my sister, my mother, and myself and Aunt Rose to the right.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's the last we saw my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were herded, then, into some barracks, where for hours and hours, we were standing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And obviously, by then I remember being thirsty.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was no water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And were taken to-- and they told us we are being taken to a shower.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But we never saw a shower, but they started to shave off our hair.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were-- they took our clothes, incidentally, and we were thrown some dreadful rags.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we looked at it-- we couldn't see ourselves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We had no mirror.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But we could see each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it was a dreadful sight, with the shaven heads.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then, God knows how many hours, or maybe, a day later, finally, we were taken to the barracks in Auschwitz, in Lager B, where we were still together, the four of us, my mother, Aunt Rose, my sister, and myself.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that's where life started.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They didn't need us to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were not [INAUDIBLE] anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That was towards the end.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We came in with a transport of gypsies, incidentally.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I understand the poor gypsies were taken immediately to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we did not work.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
